  python3-dev \
  python3-pip \

  vcftools \
  wget \
  && \

    python3 -m pip install setproctitle pylint anybadge coverage && \
    python3 -m pip install --upgrade setuptools && \
    python3 -m pip install ./

WORKDIR /data

ENTRYPOINT ["truvari"]
